      "id": "PopularPost46037",
      "post_content": "Blue's most elegant and consistent counter spell is... Counterspell. In the days of Revised, Counterspell shared countering duties with [Spell Blast](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Spell Blast) and [Power Sink](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Power Sink) - two very good spells in their own right - but Counterspell was hands down the best. Blue mages who left two Islands untapped could often bluff their opponent into not casting important spells.",
      "posted_by": "Eppek_the_Goblin",
      "html": "<div class=\"post oddItem\" id=\"PopularPost46037\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl01_post\">Blue's most elegant and consistent counter spell is... Counterspell.  In the days of Revised, Counterspell shared countering duties with <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Spell Blast\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Spell Blast\">Spell Blast</a> and <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Power Sink\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Power Sink\">Power Sink</a> - two very good spells in their own right - but Counterspell was hands down the best.  Blue mages who left two Islands untapped could often bluff their opponent into not casting important spells.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl01_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl01_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '46037'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy525\">Eppek_the_Goblin</span>\r\n                                (1/14/2010 10:09:23 PM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl01_postRating_starRating\"><img alt=\"0.5\" src=\"../../Imag