    {
      "id": "PopularPost300699",
      "post_content": "Back when this card was in every blue deck, leaving two Islands untapped was basically the same thing as a [Time Walk](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Time Walk), your opponent would either attack or just pass the turn. They didn't like walking into a Counterspell or the more strategic play was to play a decoy spell have it countered then play the Real spell. The power that blue players exerted by just having 2 untapped Islands is amazing. Yes you didn't even have to have it in your hands to make them good. Now with [Cavern of Souls](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Cavern of Souls) I really think this card should be reprinted. ",
      "posted_by": "vantha",
      "html": "<div class=\"post evenItem\" id=\"PopularPost300699\" style=\"background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl06_post\">Back when this card was in every blue deck, leaving two Islands untapped was basically the same thing as a <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Time Walk\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Time Walk\">Time Walk</a>, your opponent would either attack or just pass the turn. They didn't like walking into a Counterspell or the more strategic play was to play a decoy spell have it countered then play the Real spell. The power that blue players exerted by just having 2 untapped Islands is amazing. Yes you didn't even have to have it in your hands to make them good.  Now with <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Cavern of Souls\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Cavern of Souls\">Cavern of Souls</a> I really think this card should be reprinted. </span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl06_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"../../Classes/Controls/#\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl06_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '300699'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                    \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy73424\">vantha</span>\r\n                                (2/19/2013 6:12:59 AM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=